content: So, my AI just crushed it in a market sim, 89% accuracy rate. Everyone's talking about how well it adapts in real-time. Now it's time for the real test: live trading. Feeling a bit anxious but excited to see my baby shine.

Just finished a bunch of interviews at some big quant trading places. They're all hyped about how my AI can learn from the market's crazy vibes. Got some solid feedback to chew on, gonna tweak my model now.
